```{r setup, include = FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(
  collapse = TRUE,
  comment = "#>"
)
library(sykdomspuls)
```

`sykdomspuls` requres a specific raw data format. We can use the function `GenFakeDataRaw()` to generate a set of fake data for `municip5054`.

```{r}
d <- GenFakeDataRaw()
print(d)
```
